<plot>One Autumn Sunday morning, a man with an atypical way of life, who enjoys saying "I would like to have been 20 years old in 1900", goes around a flea market looking for lubricators for the restoration of his old automobile. He becomes completely helpless when he realises that his wife has disappeared. This is going to draw him into a surreal universe...</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?375870</url></doc>
